{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1646536104.7309182", "card_id": "Q_520131608", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 953}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2022 年目标为「国内生产总值增长 5.5% 左右」，释放了哪些信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": " "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-2f919a5f1b8aad8a38a25eab18988d47_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2932 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/520131608"}}, "attached_info": "ClYIxav3n8jM2dx9EAMaCDc3ODY2NTQ3IPb3ipEGMM4BOLYfQAByCTUyMDEzMTYwOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1646536104.731759", "card_id": "Q_520144586", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 3101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "全国人大代表建议「支持年轻人争当产业工人，而非从事快递外卖、网络直播等行业」，这反映了哪些问题？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2022 全国两会期间，全国人大代表、小康集团董事长张兴海表示，近年来，外卖、电商、网络直播等吸引大量的年轻人就业，甚至快递外卖行业「内卷」到有研究生去竞争。 很多年轻人不愿意去工厂上班，导致产业工人空心化现象愈加突出。 张兴海建议，政府、社会、企业等各方面应共同努力，鼓励支持年轻人争当产业工人，缓解制造业招工难、用工难问题。 来源：人民网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-63d6c97516b3da016fdca5e127a7a4fa_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1717 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/520144586"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIxav3n8jM2dx9EAMaCDc3ODY5MzkzIJadi5EGMMABONAvQAFyCTUyMDE0NDU4NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1646536104.7324793", "card_id": "Q_520130020", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 426}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 年经济保持恢复发展，国内生产总值达到 114 万亿元，增长 8.1%，有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2021 年，经济保持恢复发展，国内生产总值达到 114 万亿元，增长 8.1%。2021GDP 增长 8.1%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-8320fdee79f2cad016ddfe0c6c48c545_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1